                <div>Steam | Giveaway | Points | Level | Steam Store<br/>:-: | :-: | :-: | :-:<br/>[LINE][[NAME]]([STEAM]) | [SHORT-URL] | [POINTS]P | [LEVEL]+[/LINE]</div>
